name: toStringWithDefault
desc: Converts value into string or returns default when value is null.

name: StringValueMap
desc:
Cross-language implementation of a map (dictionary) where all keys and values are strings.
The stored values can be converted to different types using variety of accessor methods.

name: StringValueMap
desc: Creates a new instance of the map and assigns its value.

name: operator []
desc: The value for the given key, or null if key is not in the map.

name: operator []=
desc: Associates the key with the given value.

name: append
desc: Appends new elements to this map.

name: clear
desc: Clears this map by removing all its elements.

name: clone
desc: Creates a binary clone of this object.

name: StringValueMap.fromJson
desc: Creates a new instance of the map from json.

name: fromJson
desc: Returned JSON Map object from values of this object

name: fromMaps
desc:
Creates a new AnyValueMap by merging two or more maps.
Maps defined later in the list override values from previously defined maps.

name: fromString
desc: Parses semicolon-separated key-value pairs and returns them as a StringValueMap.

name: fromTuples
desc: Creates a new StringValueMap from a list of key-value pairs called tuples.

name: fromTuplesArray
desc:
Creates a new StringValueMap from a list of key-value pairs called tuples.
The method is similar to fromTuples but tuples are passed as array instead of parameters.

name: fromValue
desc: Converts specified value into StringValueMap.

name: get
desc: Gets a map element specified by its key.

name: getAsArray
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValueArray or returns empty AnyValueArray if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsArrayWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValueArray or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsBoolean
desc: Converts map element into a boolean or returns false if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsBooleanWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a boolean or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsDateTime
desc: Converts map element into a DateTime or returns the current date if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsDateTimeWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a DateTime or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsDouble
desc: Converts map element into a double or returns 0 if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsDoubleWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a double or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsDuration
desc: Converts map element into a Duration or returns the current date if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsDurationWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a Duration or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsFloat
desc: Converts map element into a float or returns 0 if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsFloatWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a flot or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsInteger
desc: Converts map element into an integer or returns 0 if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsIntegerWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into an integer or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsLong
desc: Converts map element into a long or returns 0 if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsLongWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a long or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsMap
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValueMap or returns empty AnyValueMap if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsMapWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValueMap or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableArray
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValueArray or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableBoolean
desc: Converts map element into a boolean or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableDateTime
desc: Converts map element into a DateTime or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableDouble
desc: Converts map element into a double or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableDuration
desc: Converts map element into a Duration or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableFloat
desc: Converts map element into a float or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableInteger
desc: Converts map element into an integer or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableLong
desc: Converts map element into a long or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableMap
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValueMap or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableString
desc: Converts map element into a string or returns null if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsNullableType
desc:
Converts map element into a value defined by specied typecode.
If conversion is not possible it returns null.

name: getAsObject
desc:
Gets the value stored in map element without any conversions.
When element key is not defined it returns the entire map value.

name: getAsString
desc: Converts map element into a string or returns '' if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsStringWithDefault
desc: Converts map element into a string or returns default value if conversion is not possible.

name: getAsType
desc:
Converts map element into a value defined by specied typecode.
If conversion is not possible it returns default value for the specified type.

name: getAsTypeWithDefault
desc:
Converts map element into a value defined by specied typecode.
If conversion is not possible it returns default value.

name: getAsValue
desc: Converts map element into an AnyValue or returns an empty AnyValue if conversion is not possible.

name: getKeys
desc: Gets keys of all elements stored in this map.

name: getValue
desc: Gets an map with values.

name: innerValue
desc: Returned inner values in Map object

name: keys
desc: The keys of this.

name: put
desc: Puts a new value into map element specified by its key.

name: remove
desc: Removes key and its associated value, if present, from the map.

name: setAsObject
desc:
Sets a new value to map element specified by its index.
When the index is not defined, it resets the entire map value.
This method has double purpose because method overrides are not supported in JavaScript.

name: toJson
desc: Initialize this object from JSON Map object

name: toString
desc:
Gets a string representation of the object.
The result is a semicolon-separated list of key-value pairs as
'key1=value1;key2=value2;key=value3'

name: TypeCode
desc:
Codes for the data types that can be
converted using TypeConverter.

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: TypeConverter
desc:
Converts arbitrary values into objects specific by TypeCodes.
For each TypeCode this class calls corresponding converter which applies
extended conversion rules to convert the values.

name: asString
desc: Converts a TypeCode into its string name.

name: toNullableType
desc: Converts value into an object type specified by Type Code or returns null when conversion is not possible.

name: toType
desc: Converts value into an object type specified by Type Code or returns type default when conversion is not possible.

name: toTypeCode
desc: Gets TypeCode for specific value.

name: toTypeWithDefault
desc: Converts value into an object type specified by Type Code or returns default value when conversion is not possible.

name: TypeDescriptor
desc:
Descriptor that points to specific object type by it's name
and optional library (or module) where this type is defined.

name: TypeDescriptor
desc: Creates a new instance of the type descriptor and sets its values.

name: equals
desc:
Compares this descriptor to a value.
If the value is also a TypeDescriptor it compares their name and library fields.
Otherwise this method returns false.

name: fromString
desc:
Parses a string to get descriptor fields and returns them as a Descriptor.
The string must have format name,library

name: getLibrary
desc: Gets the name of the library or module where the object type is defined.

name: getName
desc: Get the name of the object type.

name: toString
desc:
Gets a string representation of the object.
The result has format name,library

name: TypeMatcher
desc: Helper class matches value types for equality.

name: matchType
desc:
Matches expected type to an actual type.
The types can be specified as types, type names or TypeCode.

name: matchTypeByName
desc: Matches expected type to an actual type.

name: matchValueType
desc:
Matches expected type to a type of a value.
The expected type can be specified by a type, type name or TypeCode.

name: matchValueTypeByName
desc: Matches expected type to a type of a value.

name: TypeReflector
desc: Helper class to perform object type introspection and object instantiation.

name: createInstance
desc:
Creates an instance of an object type specified by its name
and library where it is defined.

name: createInstanceByDescriptor
desc: Creates an instance of an object type specified by type descriptor.

name: createInstanceByType
desc: Creates an instance of an object type.

name: getType
desc: Gets object type by its name and library where it is defined.

name: getTypeByDescriptor
desc: Gets object type by type descriptor.

name: isPrimitive
desc: Checks if value has primitive type.

name: UnauthorizedException
desc: Access errors caused by missing user identity (authentication error) or incorrect security permissions (authorization error).

name: UnauthorizedException
desc: Creates an error instance and assigns its values.

name: UnknownException
desc: Unknown or unexpected errors.

name: UnknownException
desc: Creates an error instance and assigns its values.

name: UnsupportedException
desc: Errors caused by calls to unsupported or not yet implemented functionality.

name: UnsupportedException
desc: Creates an error instance and assigns its values.
